h3 Intro

p.
  The <code>autocomplete</code> block is used to style form an autocomplete
  control.

p.
  It consists of a child <code>control</code> block and an
  <code>autocomplete-container</code> element with it's
  <code>autocomplete-item</code> children.

p.
  Use it to style your own autocomplete elements.

